name: 3D - Ethereal Rain: 01
description:
Lava molds to skin and breathes the day
To seize black clay and shape
Empires rising from sand.

Crystalline turquoise crash into symphony
Along Cuban shores.

The sun catches autumn leaves
Through slivers of tree gaps,
Campers watch the day pass.

-----------------------------------------------------------------

It has 2 effects:

1. The image it is!
2. If you have some 3D glasses lying around, try one on and look at the image! Just make sure that you are using the retro 3D glasses. The red and blue kind.

The image in 3D creates depth and a portal into the image to make it look like a window into a new dimension! So if you want get the 3D glasses and try it out!

Width: 900px
Hight: 900px

Original Image: 7968 x 5320
Exposure Time: 1/640s
Focal Length: 20mm
ISO Speed: 100
F-Stop: f/1.8
